title: Joaquin adds to dangerous flood situation in Mid-Atlantic
text:
Published By: CBS News: U.S. - Today 
Rain and wind from Hurricane Joaquin are adding to the already dangerous flood situation caused by a nor'easter in the Mid-Atlantic states...
